President John Magufuli has today appointed Brigadier General Gabriel Sauli Mhidize as new Director General of Medical Stores Department (MSD) . The statement from the Directorate of Presidential Communications at State House said Brig.Gen Dr Mhidize replaces Lauren Rugambwa whose appointment has been revoked. Before the appointment Brig.Gen Dr Mhidize was head of Lugalo Hospital. The appointments is with immediate effect.